        <footnote id="F4">Each restricted stock unit represents a contingent right to receive one share of common stock of Tetraphase Pharmaceuticals, Inc. for no consideration.</footnote>
        <footnote id="F5">The restricted stock units shall be eligible to vest upon achievement of certain performance conditions and, if such conditions are met, shall vest on various dates beginning no earlier than March 1, 2020 and ending no later than March 1, 2022.</footnote>
